    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度将宣布世界上最大规模选举的投票日期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-15/india-to-announce-polling-dates-for-world-s-biggest-elections</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度选举委员会将于周六宣布全国投票的日期，正式启动世界上最大民主国家的竞选活动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-15/india-to-announce-polling-dates-for-world-s-biggest-elections</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 15 Mar 2024 07:28:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登反对竞标后，新日铁捍卫美国协议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-14/nippon-steel-defends-us-deal-after-biden-comes-out-against-bid</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新日铁公司表示，尽管美国总统乔·拜登表示该公司应留在美国手中，但该公司仍决心以 141 亿美元完成对美国钢铁公司的收购。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-14/nippon-steel-defends-us-deal-after-biden-comes-out-against-bid</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 14 Mar 2024 23:41:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马克龙警告称，如果俄罗斯在乌克兰获胜，欧洲将成为下一个目标</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-14/macron-warns-european-security-would-be-lost-if-russia-wins-war</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国总统马克龙警告说，除非普京的军队在乌克兰被击败，否则欧盟将面临俄罗斯入侵的“生存”威胁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-14/macron-warns-european-security-would-be-lost-if-russia-wins-war</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 14 Mar 2024 20:38:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国瞄准外国所有权，RedBird 考虑出售电报</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-14/redbird-considers-telegraph-sale-as-uk-targets-foreign-state-ownership</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在 Rishi Sunak 政府表示正在努力禁止外国国家拥有英国媒体所有权后，RedBird IMI 正在考虑出售《电讯报》，从而有效阻止了其阿联酋支持的收购要约。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-14/redbird-considers-telegraph-sale-as-uk-targets-foreign-state-ownership</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 14 Mar 2024 20:38:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>莫迪的政党是现已被禁止的选举债券的最大受益者</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-14/modi-s-party-biggest-beneficiary-of-now-banned-electoral-bonds</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一家鲜为人知的印度彩票公司是过去五年中现已被禁止的选举债券的最大买家，这引发了人们对世界上最大民主国家的政治捐助资金的质疑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-14/modi-s-party-biggest-beneficiary-of-now-banned-electoral-bonds</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 14 Mar 2024 17:53:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国特使称中国对 TikTok 法案的愤怒“极具讽刺意味”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-14/china-s-protest-of-tiktok-bill-supremely-ironic-us-envoy-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国驻华高级外交官猛烈抨击了北京方面反对在美国禁止 TikTok 的做法，他的尖锐评论凸显了尽管两国关系最近有所改善，但两国之间持续紧张的关系。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-14/china-s-protest-of-tiktok-bill-supremely-ironic-us-envoy-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 14 Mar 2024 12:43:37 GMT</pubDate>
